Your problem is most likely related to timing.<br />To put it bluntly, writing to KON/KOFF in fast succession causes problems.<br />Refer to <a href="http://www.pcedev.net/docs/brr/apudsp.txt" class="postlink">Anomie's S-DSP Doc</a>.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3581">d4s</a> — Sun Sep 18, 2011 3:48 am</p><hr />
